snippet.title: The Guides – Available Now
snippet.description:
Now available on Apple, Google, and Amazon App Stores. Download and play: http://theguidesapp.com/download

The Guides is a cryptic journey consisting of hundreds of extremely challenging puzzles, interactive ciphers and visual riddles that are guaranteed to pleasantly frustrate your wit and test your ingenuity.

As you explore deeper, you’ll begin to unravel the enigma of The Guides, and perhaps reveal the true purpose of these mysterious messages.
